{"tid":1742040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"20191121 民間記者會","createTime":"2019-11-20T15:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T04:45:44.000Z","uid":160693,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ceed8f39172a0b864e88b862548a1d83b1c3ecd4","tid":1742040,"uid":160693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會採訪通知<br />\n<br />\n就近日林鄭月娥政權攻擊及圍堵多間大學事件及所造成之人道災難，民間記者會將作出有關回應。是次主題為「魔警圍城 萬人援救 和勇聯手 黎明起義」，現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年11月21日（星期四)<br />\n時間：晚上6時30分<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，如有查詢可向金先生查詢。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019年11月20日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/citizenspresscon/643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon%2F643&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=96b51208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/citizenspresscon/643</a>"},{"pid":"738fbf97ebab1306a1b534288b472cabf1ad57a7","tid":1742040,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:09:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"501007232f29de333d8984ce1465b15da4e402de","tid":1742040,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b5dffe730847454e00278dfb28012ae4831c4ac","tid":1742040,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"借過位<br />\n[多圖]11.21 曙光行動2.0，721 4.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e94aace41e99c122d5aaf12b98d6221cfc1b2fc","tid":1742040,"uid":160693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb057afc3552d9174f1d97e5de2df3ef6033e0c","tid":1742040,"uid":293741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"